        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Decanter Centrifuge &mdash; Coarse Desludging</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-text-light mb-3">A <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">decanter centrifuge</a> handles the first stage, removing bulk sludge including char and large metal particles from the crude pyrolysis oil. Decanters can handle particles up to 1/2" in size and feeds with up to 50% solids by volume.</p>
      <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 text-text-muted ml-4">
        <li>&#8226; Max solids: up to 50% (v/v)</li>
        <li>&#8226; Max particle size: 1/2"</li>
        <li>&#8226; Min particle separated: 50 &micro;m</li>
        <li>&#8226; Capacity: 10 to 350+ GPM</li>
        <li>&#8226; Mode: Continuous</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 shadow-sm">
